==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Immersed
<hw>Im*mersed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>p. p. & a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Deeply plunged into anything, especially a fluid.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Deeply occupied; engrossed; entangled.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Growing wholly under water.</def>
<rj><au>Gray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Immersible</ent>⟦br⟧
